@startuml
autonumber

title Codebeamer Automation Suite - 업로드 시퀀스 (v2)

actor User
participant "CLI (`cli_main_v2`)" as CLI
participant "업로드 Wizard (`CodebeamerUploadWizardV2`)" as Wizard
participant "Excel 처리기 (`ExcelHierarchyProcessor`)" as Processor
participant "매핑 서비스 (`MappingServiceV2`)" as Mapper
participant "Codebeamer 클라이언트" as Client
participant "Codebeamer API" as API

User -> CLI : CLI 실행
CLI -> Wizard : load_projects()
Wizard -> Client : get_projects()
Client -> API : GET /v3/projects
API --> Client : projects
Client --> Wizard : projects
Wizard --> CLI : projects
CLI -> User : 프로젝트 선택 요청

CLI -> Wizard : select_project(project_id)
CLI -> Wizard : load_trackers()
Wizard -> Client : get_trackers(project_id)
Client -> API : GET /v3/projects/{project_id}/trackers
API --> Client : trackers
Client --> Wizard : trackers
Wizard --> CLI : trackers
CLI -> User : 트래커 선택 요청
CLI -> Wizard : select_tracker(tracker_id)

CLI -> Wizard : read_excel(file_path, sheet_name, list_cols)
Wizard -> Processor : read_excel(...)
Processor --> Wizard : raw_df
Wizard -> Processor : merge_multiline_records(raw_df, list_cols)
Processor --> Wizard : merged_df
Wizard -> Processor : add_hierarchy_by_indent(merged_df)
Processor --> Wizard : hierarchy_df
Wizard -> Processor : build_upload_df(hierarchy_df, list_cols)
Processor --> Wizard : upload_df

CLI -> Wizard : load_schema_and_compare(selected_mapping)
Wizard -> Client : get_tracker_schema(tracker_id)
Client -> API : GET /v3/trackers/{tracker_id}/schema
API --> Client : schema
Client --> Wizard : schema
Wizard -> Mapper : flatten_schema_fields(schema)
Mapper --> Wizard : schema_df
Wizard -> Mapper : compare_upload_df_with_schema(upload_df, schema_df, selected_mapping)
Mapper --> Wizard : comparison_df
Wizard --> CLI : comparison_df

CLI -> Wizard : process_option_mapping(selected_mapping)
Wizard -> Mapper : get_option_field_candidates(schema_df)
Mapper --> Wizard : option_candidates_df
Wizard -> Mapper : build_option_maps_from_schema(schema_df)
Mapper --> Wizard : option_maps
Wizard -> Mapper : check_option_alignment(upload_df, option_mapping, option_maps)
Mapper --> Wizard : option_check_df
Wizard -> Mapper : apply_option_resolution(upload_df, option_mapping, option_maps)
Mapper --> Wizard : converted_upload_df
Wizard --> CLI : selected_option_mapping, option_check_df

CLI -> Wizard : preview_payload(row_id)
Wizard -> Wizard : TrackerItemBase 구성
Wizard -> Wizard : TableFieldValue 및 payload 직렬화
Wizard --> CLI : payload dict 반환

CLI -> Wizard : upload(dry_run)
loop Parent 우선 순서로 각 row 처리
  Wizard -> Wizard : preview_payload(row_id)
  alt dry run
    Wizard --> CLI : 가상 result id
  else 실제 업로드
    Wizard -> Client : create_item(tracker_id, payload, parent_item_id)
    Client -> API : POST /v3/trackers/{tracker_id}/items
    API --> Client : created item
    Client --> Wizard : created item
  end
end

Wizard --> CLI : upload_result
CLI -> Wizard : save_state(output_dir)
Wizard --> CLI : 산출물 저장 완료
@enduml
